    "description": "<strong>“如果能回到过去，一定会把同伴们救出来。。。”<br>出现在我们面前的奇迹之蝶</strong><br><br>埋藏在心中已久的真心终于爆发的瞬间，‘顺姬’的身上发生了能回到1945年的奇迹。回到了同伴们消失前一天的‘顺姬’，需要找到线索解开谜团改变命运。但每一次找到新的线索时，都会面对意想不到的真相。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <u>这个故事根据真实事件改编。</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/3902f14e037791af5896698e0bfbddcb.poster.avif?t=1658851093\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/3902f14e037791af5896698e0bfbddcb.webm?t=1658851093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/3902f14e037791af5896698e0bfbddcb.mp4?t=1658851093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[GAME PLAY]</strong></h2>‘星期三’是为了阻止1945年那一天发生的悲剧，在过去与现在之间进行穿梭寻找隐秘记录的点击式3D严肃游戏。随着填满‘顺姬’的手册，真相也会离大家越来越近。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[FEATURE]</strong></h2></li><li>台词，道具，提示都经过了详细考证的严肃游戏<br></li><li>1945年与1992年，完整的呈现了时代感与氛围的3D画面<br></li><li>加强代入感的细致剧情与 背景音乐<br></li><li>计划支持多国语言<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/5333de6f271b6851af7d0a5bb0ba4ee2.poster.avif?t=1658851093\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/5333de6f271b6851af7d0a5bb0ba4ee2.webm?t=1658851093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1119610/extras/5333de6f271b6851af7d0a5bb0ba4ee2.mp4?t=1658851093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为了实现人生唯一的愿望而穿越时间，本游戏是根据真实事件为基础改编的严肃游戏。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现在邀请您进入充满探险与解谜的3D世界。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在地狱之岛寻找隐藏的线索改变未来，拯救未来的旅程即将开始。</h2></li></ul>",
